SubjectOrder Amending the 19th Meeting of the Parties to the Montreal Protocol Privileges and Immunities Order
PrecisOrder Amending the 19TH MEETING OF THE PARTIES TO THE MONTREAL PROTOCOL PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER, in order to correct an error raised by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations by abrogating from subsection 2(3) of the Order made in 2007 the reference to section 26 of Article VII of the Convention on the Privileges and Immunities of the United Nations.
